<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="idbbb38c12-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa" identifier="/us/usc/t42/s1997i"><num value="1997i">§ 1997i.</num><heading> Disclaimer respecting standards of care</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">Provisions of this subchapter shall not authorize promulgation of regulations defining standards of care.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="idbbb38c13-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa">(<ref href="/us/pl/96/247/s11">Pub. L. 96–247, § 11</ref>, <date date="1980-05-23">May 23, 1980</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/94/354">94 Stat. 354</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
